n=int(input('enter n value:'))
factorial=1
sum=1
for i in range(1,n+1):
    factorial=factorial*i
    sum=sum+factorial 
print('the sum of factorials is:',sum)
Output: 
enter n value:100
the sum of factorials is: 94269001683709979260859834124473539872070722613982672442938359305624678223479506023400294093599136466986609124347432647622826870038220556442336528920420940314
>
